OL,3,CHalf a million people miss out on
OL,4,Cchild benefit payment after glitch
OL,6,FITV News' reporter Olivia Guthrie has
OL,7,Fthe latest from outside the HMRC
OL,8,Foffices in central London.
OL,10,FAround half a million people have been
OL,11,Faffected by an issue which meant that
OL,12,Fsome child payments did not arrive as
OL,13,Fscheduled.
OL,15,FAround 30% of child benefit payments
OL,16,Fscheduled for Monday were not made `
OL,17,Fequating to around 500,000 people
OL,18,Fbeing affected.
