OL,3,CHalf a million people miss out on
OL,4,Cchild benefit payment after glitch
OL,6,FHM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) has
OL,7,Fapologised and said it is working
OL,8,Furgently to resolve the issue.
OL,10,FAn HMRC spokesperson said: "We're
OL,11,Fsorry that some customers' child
OL,12,Fbenefit payments have not arrived as
OL,13,Fscheduled and we are working urgently
OL,14,Fto resolve the issue.
OL,16,F"The issues that caused payment
OL,17,Fproblems today will not impact
OL,18,Fpayments scheduled for tomorrow."
OL,20,FChild benefit is usually paid every
OL,21,Ffour weeks on a Monday or a Tuesday.
